# Tiling
## Focusing
alt + ctrl - k : yabai -m window --focus prev || yabai -m window --focus last  # focus prev or last window
alt + ctrl - j : yabai -m window --focus next || yabai -m window --focus first # focus next or first window

alt + ctrl - s : yabai -m display --focus 1 # focus monitor 1
alt + ctrl - d : yabai -m display --focus 2 # focus monitor 2
alt + ctrl - f : yabai -m display --focus 3 # focus monitor 3

## Moving
alt + ctrl - o : yabai -m window --swap first && yabai -m window --focus first # move focused window around on same monitor

alt + ctrl - w : yabai -m window --display 1 && yabai -m display --focus 1 # move focused window to monitor 1
alt + ctrl - e : yabai -m window --display 2 && yabai -m display --focus 2 # move focused window to monitor 2
alt + ctrl - r : yabai -m window --display 3 && yabai -m display --focus 3 # move focused window to monitor 3

## Layout
cmd + shift - space : yabai -m window --toggle split # toggle between horizontal & vertical splits
alt + ctrl - z : yabai -m space --balance            # balance window sizes

alt + ctrl - h : yabai -m window --resize left:-80:0 || yabai -m window --resize right:-80:0 # shrink focused window horizontally
alt + ctrl - l : yabai -m window --resize left:80:0 || yabai -m window --resize right:80:0   # grow focused window horizontally
